# Cloudflare Pages-style redirects for the AAL bug bounty.
#
# When this directory is deployed as a separate Pages project (or its files
# are merged into the main sameasyou.ai deploy), the canonical URL is
# `https://sameasyou.ai/bounty`. Make both `/bounty` and `/bounty/` resolve
# to bounty.html, and keep deep links stable.

/bounty           /bounty.html   200
/bounty/          /bounty.html   200
/bounty/index     /bounty.html   301
/bounty/index.html /bounty.html  301
